511
00:19:32,208 --> 00:19:33,500
Is that all?

512
00:19:33,583 --> 00:19:34,958
Are you kidding me?

513
00:19:35,041 --> 00:19:36,791
If that's the kind of
work you want me to do,

514
00:19:36,875 --> 00:19:38,333
then I'm not gonna--

515
00:19:38,416 --> 00:19:40,250
[MEIKO]
Not gonna what?

516
00:19:40,333 --> 00:19:42,875
