has been pigging out on?

524
00:19:59,833 --> 00:20:02,375
--Not to mention--
--[SHINGO groans]

525
00:20:02,458 --> 00:20:04,791
When they learn how
trustworthy you are.

526
00:20:04,875 --> 00:20:06,541
Just keep going the
way you've been going,

527
00:20:06,625 --> 00:20:08,375
