534
00:20:23,791 --> 00:20:25,208
You look so thin!

535
00:20:25,291 --> 00:20:28,000
So, were they starving
you down in solitary?

536
00:20:28,083 --> 00:20:30,375
Nah, I got three squares a day.

537
00:20:30,458 --> 00:20:32,333
[coughs] I even got dessert.

538
00:20:32,416 --> 00:20:34,208
