00:20:38,625 --> 00:20:40,541
Right! My bad.

543
00:20:40,625 --> 00:20:42,833
[KIYOSHI] Aww man, she's
giving me the stink eye.

544
00:20:42,916 --> 00:20:46,041
She must be pissed about
what went down at the clinic.

545
00:20:46,125 --> 00:20:47,791
[HANA]
I remember everything up until

