551
00:21:03,333 --> 00:21:04,666
[KIYOSHI]
Huh?

552
00:21:04,750 --> 00:21:07,125
I said bring it.

553
00:21:07,208 --> 00:21:08,416
[KIYOSHI]
Here we go again.

554
00:21:08,500 --> 00:21:10,083
[JOE]
Get it yourself.

555
00:21:10,166 --> 00:21:12,250
Hey, bro, what the hell's
the matter with you?

556
00:21:12,333 --> 00:21:14,291
--He screwed all of us over!
--I think you've been acting

557
00:21:14,375 --> 00:21:16,416
