for long enough.

558
00:21:16,500 --> 00:21:17,333
Shut your piehole.

559
00:21:17,416 --> 00:21:18,416
[SHINGO grunts]

560
00:21:20,166 --> 00:21:21,291
[SHINGO grunts]

561
00:21:21,375 --> 00:21:23,083
