Uh...

562
00:21:24,958 --> 00:21:25,916
[MEIKO]
Break's over!

563
00:21:26,000 --> 00:21:28,541
Back to work, now!

564
00:21:28,625 --> 00:21:29,250
[SHINGO]
Tch.

565
00:21:29,333 --> 00:21:30,333
[MEIKO]
Hey, Shingo.

566
00:21:30,416 --> 00:21:31,625
--[SHINGO gasps]
