567
00:21:31,708 --> 00:21:34,541
I have a different
job in store for you.

568
00:21:34,625 --> 00:21:36,041
Yes, ma'am.

569
00:21:43,708 --> 00:21:44,958
[JOE]
Want some?

570
00:21:47,208 --> 00:21:48,708
Sure, thanks.

571
00:21:50,416 --> 00:21:52,416
