596
00:22:44,375 --> 00:22:45,791
what they were
saying to each other,

597
00:22:45,875 --> 00:22:48,958
but I definitely
think I got the gist.

598
00:22:49,041 --> 00:22:49,833
[SHINGO]
Wait...

599
00:22:49,916 --> 00:22:51,666
